headline: Goldman Sachs Maintains Buy on Salesforce After Agentforce 3.0 Launch
summary: Salesforce, Inc. (NYSE:CRM) ranks among the best fundamental stocks to buy according to hedge funds. Goldman Sachs maintained its $385 price target and Buy rating on Salesforce, Inc. (NYSE:CRM) on June 24 in response to the company’s Agentforce 3.0 launch. The investment bank claims that transparency, compatibility, and time-to-value are all significantly improved by the […]
